{"word":"G1773 - ἔννυχον - énnychon - en'-noo-khon - Before day","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔννυχον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">énnychon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en'-noo-khon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Before day</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இருட்டான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"nightly, nocturnal"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G3571 - νύξ - nýx - noox/3571\">G3571</a>; (adverbially) <i>by night:</i> - before day.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}